; Hub — cleanup pass on Wave 2.
;   - ParallaxBackground keeps only a nebula far layer; the silhouette
;     skyline was tried and pulled — it read as a landscape and clashed
;     with the cosmic Hub vibe.
;   - The giant clock from a previous pass was tried and pulled too;
;     it didn't land tonally.
;   - Each door uses a richer arch texture with a baked-in radial void
;     interior, an inner rim glow, and a small carved keystone at the
;     apex. No per-door spinning overlay; the gradient is in the art.
;   - Fog band, fireflies, door bob animation, door collision /
;     interaction wiring, and Curiosity / TouchControls instances are
;     unchanged.
